(3136, '_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e', '<h4>Most Popular</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce/''>WooCommerce - excelling eCommerce</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=woocommerce&amp;_wpnonce=a33ae50530&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''WooCommerce - excelling eCommerce''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>WooCommerce is a powerful, extendable eCommerce plugin that helps you sell anything. Beautifully.</p>\n<h4>Newest Plugins</h4>\n<h5><a href=''http://wordpress.org/plugins/ram108-sape/''>SAPE Links</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=ram108-sape&amp;_wpnonce=9aafc4bdd3&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''SAPE Links''>Install</a>)</span>\n<p>SAPE.RU: Adds widget and shortcode to integrate sape.ru contextual links for Russian webmasters.</p>\n', 'no'),
